Class EditHabitEventTest

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    junit.framework.Test

    public class EditHabitEventTest
extends android.test.ActivityInstrumentationTestCase2<LoginActivity>
    A class for testing the ability to edit existing habit events. Note that this class does not test the ability to edit images, since solo/robotium cannot navigate Android system UI. These tests assume that there is a Jogging Habit in the database with a start date of April 20, 2016. Without this, some or all of these tests may fail.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    amckerna
